OL,5,MCovid, alcohol ban after 21            
OL,6,M                                       
OL,8, In Piedmont from October 18 the sale   
OL,9, of alcohol will be prohibited after    
OL,10, 9 pm.                                  
OL,13, Furthermore, all retail business with  
OL,14, the exception of pharmacies will be    
OL,15, closed at night  (from midnight to     
OL,16, 5 am).                                 
OL,19, The new ordinance will be valid until  
OL,20, November 13, 2020.                     
